description:
UEL.Highlights.2016-03-10.ITV.HDTV.1080p.2ch.x265.10bit.[S-Less]

Mark Pougatch presents action from the last-16 first-leg ties, as the teams attempted to secure an advantage ahead of the second-leg matches that will take place next week. Fixtures included Liverpool v Manchester United at Anfield, and Borussia Dortmund v Tottenham Hotspur at Signal Iduna Park. Presented by Mark Pougatch and Jacqui Oatley, with analysis from Robbie Fowler, Louis Saha and Glenn Hoddle, and commentary by Clive Tyldesley and Sam Matterface
